{"tid":2359337,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"探子TG: ISP 硬件上一早ready 封網","createTime":"2021-01-08T21:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T02:42:10.000Z","uid":33336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb6e518143c753d067ca501c42df0f1faca69d6","tid":2359337,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:57:51.000Z","msg":"【香港電訊員工：硬件一早已經ready封網】<br />\n<br />\n有香港電訊寬頻部門工作的員工向本台爆料，該公司由過去ADSL技術升級至FTTH時已引入中國公司的解決方案，在硬件上已支援網絡封鎖及流量分析。前者用途除商業考慮封鎖某粒ip之外，過去HKT亦都有多次應警方要求封鎖和限制特定連線，有關動作除了使用「網上行」客戶受影響外，手提電話供應商例如1010丶csl丶Sun mobile丶中國移動3G這些同樣使用香港電訊作為傳輸線路嘅公司都一樣會受影響。流量分析可以得知用戶使用寬頻的習慣，好像影片串流還是傾向電競用途，過去亦有使用客戶上網習慣制定公司銷售成人收費服務的策略。很明顯這些數據也有利於社會監控。<br />\n<br />\n//用數碼通定中國移動其實都係同一條線路//<br />\n<br />\n根據該員工指出，香港寬頻也同樣有為手提電話供應商提供傳輸線路，包括數碼通丶中國移動丶自由鳥等。當香港寬頻對某些存取進行封鎖，手提電話網絡也同樣受牽連。香港現時並沒有自行鋪線路的手提電話網絡商。￼<br />\n<br />\n本台記者翻查相關公司的新聞稿支持￼￼本港的手提電話供應商￼￼￼是依賴傳統固網供應商提供線路的說法。￼<a href=\"https://www.smartoneholdings.com/about/media_centre/press_release/press/2020/04/2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartoneholdings.com%2Fabout%2Fmedia_centre%2Fpress_release%2Fpress%2F2020%2F04%2F2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXXdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=216a8e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smartoneholdings.com/about/media_centre/press_release/press/2020/04/2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n該員工也提到他們進行測試時發現如果用戶端成功連接VPN，流量分析的統計便會失效。而用戶家中的Modem也能被公司遠端操作達致封鎖部份連線，現時公司把這個功能用於提醒繳交欠款，用戶裝置上網時會被轉向到繳費提醒頁面，直至你確認收到通知相關限制才會解除。<br />\n<br />\n插圖：風傳媒<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n報道各區突發資訊 捍衛公眾利益<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cumediahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcumediahk%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXXdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=e9322090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cumediahk/</a><br />\nInstagram：@cu.mediahk<br />\n報料熱線：9881 6992<br />\n<br />\n課金支持：<br />\nFPS: info@cumediahk.org"},{"pid":"b49788ab8eccc4b3a0273f13d7091a0107ebb684","tid":2359337,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:04:47.000Z","msg":"share去twitter戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要話比美國知支那既陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43836aba067cbd5e83775c518ef2df029096781c","tid":2359337,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:08:35.000Z","msg":"最低限度用VPN"},{"pid":"35a2fb9fc4d20703e1cd4de5572d0b2b5cca985d","tid":2359337,"uid":249708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"唔識IT既嚇死<br />\n識IT既笑死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c5ab91b7ee2fba22e634ecb7b4ab5621ca9fbf","tid":2359337,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a2fb9fc4d20703e1cd4de5572d0b2b5cca985d","tid":2359337,"uid":249708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"唔識IT既嚇死<br />\n識IT既笑死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"即係你識IT？不如講下發生咩事"},{"pid":"16575348dae7f118aaf764b9ed572d3cd1f24a1f","tid":2359337,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"352c072fa5b4394732d6e2f6069c8085b2e576bd","tid":2359337,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35a2fb9fc4d20703e1cd4de5572d0b2b5cca985d","tid":2359337,"uid":249708,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"唔識IT既嚇死<br />\n識IT既笑死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"不如分享多d<br />\n等唔識既都學下野"},{"p